<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>WEARiT - About Us</title>
        <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
        <link
            href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />
        <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->
        <link
            href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
                color: #212529;
            }

            .promo-banner {
                background-color: #000;
                color: #fff;
                padding: 8px 0;
                font-size: 14px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .navbar {
                padding: 15px 0;
            }

            .navbar-brand {
                font-weight: 700;
                font-size: 24px;
                color: #000;
            }

            .nav-link {
                color: #000;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin: 0 15px;
            }

            .search-input {
                border-radius: 20px;
                border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
                padding: 8px 15px;
            }

            .icon-button {
                background: none;
                border: none;
                color: #000;
                margin-left: 15px;
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .breadcrumb {
                font-size: 14px;
                color: #6c757d;
                margin-top: 30px;
            }

            .breadcrumb-item a {
                color: #6c757d;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .breadcrumb-item.active {
                color: #212529;
            }

            .about-section {
                padding: 60px 0;
            }

            .about-section h1 {
                font-weight: 700;
                font-size: 48px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .about-section p {
                font-size: 18px;
                line-height: 1.7;
                color: #6c757d;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

            .about-image {
                border-radius: 10px;
                box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                object-fit: cover;
            }

            .subscription-section {
                background-color: #f8f9fa;
                padding: 50px 0;
            }

            .subscription-form {
                border-radius: 25px;
                overflow: hidden;
                display: flex;
                max-width: 500px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }

            .subscription-input {
                flex: 1;
                border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
                border-radius: 25px 0 0 25px;
                padding: 15px 20px;
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .subscription-button {
                background-color: #000;
                color: #fff;
                border: none;
                border-radius: 0 25px 25px 0;
                padding: 15px 30px;
                font-weight: 600;
            }

            .feature-card {
                text-align: center;
                padding: 30px 15px;
                transition: all 0.3s ease;
            }

            .feature-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
            }

            .feature-icon {
                font-size: 32px;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

            .feature-title {
                font-weight: 600;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .feature-description {
                font-size: 14px;
                color: #6c757d;
            }

            .footer {
                background-color: #000;
                color: #fff;
                padding: 60px 0 20px;
            }

            .footer h5 {
                font-weight: 600;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .footer-link {
                color: #e0e0e0;
                text-decoration: none;
                display: block;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .footer-link:hover {
                color: #fff;
            }

            .social-icon {
                color: #fff;
                font-size: 20px;
                margin-right: 15px;
            }

            .copyright {
                margin-top: 40px;
                font-size: 14px;
                color: #6c757d;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <%- include('../partials/header') %>
            <div class="about-section">
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <h1>Our Story</h1>
                        <p>
                            Founded in 2015, WEARiT began with a simple vision -
                            to create clothing that combines comfort, style, and
                            sustainability. Our journey started in a small
                            studio in Brooklyn, where our founder, Emma Clarke,
                            designed the first collection featuring minimalist
                            pieces that could be worn for years.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Today, WEARiT has grown into a global brand, but our
                            core values remain unchanged. We believe in creating
                            timeless garments that transcend seasons and trends.
                            Each piece is thoughtfully designed and crafted from
                            premium materials sourced from ethical suppliers
                            around the world.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Our commitment to sustainability drives every
                            decision we make - from the fabrics we choose to the
                            packaging we use. We're not perfect, but we're
                            constantly evolving and finding new ways to reduce
                            our environmental footprint while creating beautiful
                            clothing that you'll love to wear.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <img
                            src="images/image1.jpg"
                            alt="Man wearing pastel purple formal shirt"
                            class="about-image"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.0/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>
